  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Confirmed diagnosis of Type II diabetes for at least 2 years

          -  Type 2 diabetics on oral hypoglycemic agents and/or insulin

          -  Fasting blood sugar of &gt;200mg% on at least two occasions

          -  Willing to keep a weekly diary and undergo observation for 12 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of of previous and/or acute diabetic complications such as myocardial
             infarction, CVA or nephropathy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
